OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGerman Documenta art fair  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchief quits in             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fanti-Semitism row          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The director of a world-famous German  
OL,6, art show has quit in a row over an     
OL,7, artwork condemned as anti-Semitic.     
OL,9,FThe Documenta 15 show in Kassel briefly
OL,10,Fincluded a mural showing a soldier with
OL,11,Fa pig's head and a Star of David.      
OL,13,FThe mural also depicted a character    
OL,14,Fwith fangs, Jewish Orthodox-style      
OL,15,Fsidelocks and a hat labelled "SS". It  
OL,16,Fwas done by an Indonesian art group.   
OL,18,FThere was an outcry soon after the show
OL,19,Fopened last month. Director Sabine     
OL,20,FSchormann has now resigned.            
